And I don't want you to think about
the stuff that we left behind.

01:08:34.680 --> 01:08:36.990
I want you to think
about the stuff that we have

01:08:37.080 --> 01:08:39.435
and how we can be
better prepared in the future.

01:08:39.520 --> 01:08:40.749
Okay?

