- Who is it?
- Hello, hello!

01:16:49.440 --> 01:16:52.035
Hello, is Mark there?

01:16:52.120 --> 01:16:54.191
No, there's no Mark.

01:16:59.680 --> 01:17:02.718
Can we come in? We're very cold.
